Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.99,0:00:03.84,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Up you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.84,0:00:06.31,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,And, again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.92,0:01:44.91,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.69,0:01:49.54,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.83,0:01:53.38,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Get off the counter!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.78,0:01:53.98,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.98,0:01:54.80,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.54,0:01:57.18,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,And down you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.18,0:01:58.98,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wakana, can I get some food?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:00.53,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,In a sec. I'm feeding Dora first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.92,0:02:04.77,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,For you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:05.82,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,And you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.63,0:02:09.13,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.13,0:02:10.65,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Leftovers from last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:11.70,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.70,0:02:14.82,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you always make \Ntoo much for dinner, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:18.38,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You could at least jazz it up with \Nsome egg or sauce, or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:19.60,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go now,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.60,0:02:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so please wash the dishes \Nwhen you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:22.19,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.19,0:02:23.30,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Don't "what" me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:25.12,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,And you should get up earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:27.90,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Don't click your tongue at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.03,0:02:30.50,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:34.63,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you know what happened \Nto the flowers I left here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:35.86,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I planted them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.86,0:02:36.55,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}planted{\i0} them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:37.79,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,In the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.79,0:02:38.84,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:41.14,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You looked busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.14,0:02:43.92,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I was taking those to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:45.64,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You did? When?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:47.48,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:47.76,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Have a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:49.00,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:17.25,Default,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 1\N Running and Inviting
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:17.25,Default,Title,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.61,0:03:29.22,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Sabure, whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:01.07,Default,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,Miyamoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.21,0:04:04.04,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:05.42,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,On your way to practice, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.63,0:04:09.20,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it kind of sad to play \Nbatminton by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:10.87,Default,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}bad{\i0}minton.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:13.06,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, forever alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.66,0:04:14.93,Default,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:24.25,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with taking the train home?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:26.07,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:31.70,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shirohamazaka High School
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.59,0:04:37.96,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:40.11,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Anything for our best customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:47.08,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,It's Saturday, so I'll be home early.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:48.35,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,See you in the evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:51.19,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep eating like that, you'll get fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:55.34,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off, Sabure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:58.12,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.38,0:05:10.74,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...even on a narrow path.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.22,0:05:14.54,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Running out, headlong
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:15.80,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}toward a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:19.78,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looking up, waving at the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.78,0:05:25.33,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Connecting our unstoppable feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:27.59,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Stop there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:30.18,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,You all need to listen to the other sections.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:31.68,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Sopranos, tone it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenors, mezzo-forte.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:35.05,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have to keep telling you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.05,0:05:37.27,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,There's only a month left until the recital.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.25,0:05:40.25,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,We'll work on the sections after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:41.07,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.50,0:05:46.85,Default,Ueno,0000,0000,0000,,Miyamoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.39,0:05:49.26,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:51.45,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:05:58.42,Default,Ueno,0000,0000,0000,,You want to sing, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:05:59.49,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:01.97,Default,Ueno,0000,0000,0000,,I have the song memorized,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.97,0:06:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you don't need to turn \Nthe pages for me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:04.96,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:06.60,Default,Ueno,0000,0000,0000,,This is our last performance this year,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.60,0:06:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so why don't you talk \Nto the vice principal?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:11.05,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Great idea! I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:26.82,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Sakai-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:29.32,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:32.14,Default,Saka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh wow, your plant is really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:33.28,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Are those fresh flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:34.10,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:36.07,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I snipped some hydrangeas from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:36.79,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:38.91,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:39.68,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.59,0:06:44.29,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Good timing, Konatsu. Help me wrap these.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.74,0:06:47.89,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, before Miss Takahashi shows up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:50.47,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,You should have done that at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.75,0:06:53.42,Default,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,Sawa, I need your help over here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.42,0:06:54.93,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, one second.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:57.55,Default,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,Konatsu, can I see your math printout?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.55,0:06:58.43,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:01.36,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are my slaves today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:08.01,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,Where in Austria did you live?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:09.05,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,In Wien.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:11.96,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,Wien? Oh, you mean Vienna.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:15.12,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I wasn't able \Nto get a uniform on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:17.26,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:19.74,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,It must be very hard to move back here
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.74,0:07:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in your third year of high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.07,0:07:24.01,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have someone show \Nyou around after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:25.57,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.45,0:07:28.74,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka! Late again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.78,0:07:32.88,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,Wait right here. I'll call you in shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.88,0:07:33.89,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.88,0:07:36.72,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,All right, class, take your seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:37.54,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,Today, we'll–
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.11,0:07:38.22,Default,Sana,0000,0000,0000,,Present bouquets!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:44.44,Default,Board,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Miss Takai \NThank You So Much!\NHave a Healthy Baby!\NBoy or Girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:44.44,Default,Board,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:47.54,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,It's just maternity leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if I'm not back by \Ngraduation, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:52.70,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Could we do our graduation ceremony right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:53.79,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.79,0:07:55.95,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,What, you wanna sing "Pomp and \NCircumstance" with everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.89,0:08:00.66,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sakai-san, would you sing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:03.40,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:04.89,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,You've been studying music, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.89,0:08:06.93,Default,Girl3,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear you sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.93,0:08:08.05,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,All right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:12.92,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,You all know who I want \Nto hear last today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.92,0:08:14.26,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,Our repeat offender.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.67,0:08:16.03,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka Taichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.03,0:08:17.22,Default,Tana,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:21.39,Default,Tana,0000,0000,0000,,I come early every morning for practice! \NI wasn't late today, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:23.23,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,Excuses, excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:24.31,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, men.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:28.27,Default,Tana,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, then I'll sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:31.84,Default,Tana,0000,0000,0000,,I will now perform Shirahamazaka \NHigh's school song.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:41.01,Default,Tana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to hear the voice \Nof the white beach,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:46.40,Default,Tana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so let's climb that winding slope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:47.67,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:49.92,Default,Tana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My dear friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:51.05,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.79,0:08:54.96,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,I've been away from Japan for twelve years,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.96,0:08:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll try my best to get \Nused to everything quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:09:00.81,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, as my only friends are books,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beseech you to bless \Nme with your favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.91,0:09:10.65,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Kneeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:13.27,Default,Radio,0000,0000,0000,,It is now noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:28.26,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka, please show him around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.26,0:09:30.32,Default,Tana,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:35.10,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:40.30,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,Sakai, can you help me carry these?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.32,0:09:42.51,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.80,0:09:46.03,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,Have you gotten used \Nto the general curriculum?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.03,0:09:46.91,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:47.77,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,And you've made some friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:49.35,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:50.75,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:52.49,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Can you please drop this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:56.48,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,If you hold out a little longer, \NI'll set you up with my kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:09:57.74,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,You're having a boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:10:00.85,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,Does it have to be a boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:02.36,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.36,0:10:03.63,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:05.08,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to grab my car keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.51,0:10:09.96,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,You came all the way here \Nto talk about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:11.37,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.37,0:10:14.57,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,I'm well aware Ueno-san has \Nthe music memorized.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:17.31,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Her focus is piano, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:20.36,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Then why do I need to \Nturn the pages for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:21.93,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Music is not a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:24.63,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,This joint recital is an \Nevent with a rich tradition,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.63,0:10:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,featuring not only the high \Nschools of this district,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:30.02,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,but professional performers \Nare invited, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:36.15,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}35th Joint Recital
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:33.22,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Professors from music colleges \Nwill also be coming to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:36.15,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,For music students, this \Nis a priceless opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.77,0:10:39.49,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Remind me, what did you do at \Nthis function last year?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:49.67,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,But that's why I've been...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:54.74,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Anybody can love music.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:58.63,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,For music to love you, however, \Nis another story entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:05.10,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,It takes a special something \Nto move people's hearts,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you don't have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:09.69,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Abandon your aspirations \Nto sing on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.69,0:11:12.10,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Once the recital is over–
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.97,0:11:12.10,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Then I quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.53,0:11:14.59,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.59,0:11:17.12,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,I quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.94,0:11:22.38,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Miyamoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.09,0:11:26.87,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,If you're serious, \Nsubmit a formal request.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.73,0:11:50.53,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,What gives you the right \Nto act like you know me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.53,0:11:53.66,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody knows if they can sing, until they try!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.66,0:11:55.80,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me just because I'm a general–
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.80,0:11:59.33,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Blergh! You cow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.15,0:12:05.17,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:08.62,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,That's it. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.19,0:12:10.70,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.70,0:12:11.96,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have your phone on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:12.92,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:18.47,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,That's my address.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.47,0:12:21.11,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,Contact me if anything comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:22.33,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.33,0:12:24.61,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,Like if you find a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.92,0:12:28.39,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,And come see the baby once it's born.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:32.55,Default,Tana,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I want to eat \Nbefore I go to club.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:34.31,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,What club?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:36.17,Default,Tana,0000,0000,0000,,Badminton.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:38.18,Default,Tana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only member right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.18,0:12:40.06,Default,Tana,0000,0000,0000,,but today I get to practice with
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.06,0:12:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my sister at her university.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:43.82,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,"Sister" is for a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.37,0:12:47.57,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,What was the word for a male sibling?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:50.58,Default,Tana,0000,0000,0000,,Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:52.32,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.32,0:12:54.19,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,I tried brushing up through books,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I've still got a lot to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:12:59.17,Default,Tana,0000,0000,0000,,Do those books explain how \Nto eat ramen, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:01.13,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:02.34,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:04.47,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't have to quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:06.68,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,She's doesn't understand anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:10.83,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go have a talk with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.83,0:13:13.23,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, Sawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:17.15,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Stop! I said, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.01,0:13:21.20,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,It's just, I'm already a senior...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:23.79,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Singing might be the most important \Nthing in my life right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.79,0:13:27.24,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,but soon I'll be graduating, \Ngoing to college, getting a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:28.82,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,These days are almost over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:33.00,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,So if she won't let me sing, \NI should just quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:35.21,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,But then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.59,0:13:38.18,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I haven't had a chance to sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:42.25,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,I really want to sing,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.73,0:13:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm going to start a new choir group.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.08,0:13:47.28,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you have to sing with me, Sawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:58.40,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Me?! But I have a terrible voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:13:59.56,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:00.52,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,You have a powerful voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:02.41,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm already doing archery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.41,0:14:03.38,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Do both.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.96,0:14:06.15,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Are you allowed to start a new club?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:07.58,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.58,0:14:08.72,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:12.68,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,You put the name of the club \Nand what it's for here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.68,0:14:14.88,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,Here, you put the president, \Nand here the advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:17.41,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,You need the principal's seal here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:19.29,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you submit this \Nto the student council
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with the club members' applications.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.12,0:14:22.06,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.06,0:14:24.26,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,You need at least five people to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:25.59,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:27.96,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,I've got myself and Sawa,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.96,0:14:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I was thinking I \Ncould invite Sakai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:33.06,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,She'd be great to have on board!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:33.95,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.51,0:14:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This might not be a good time, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:38.81,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:41.98,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she didn't have enough \Ngeneral credits,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so she's taking supplementary classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:50.28,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,But a girl like you might be \Na good catalyst for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.75,0:14:52.45,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,A girl like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:54.80,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,A cheerful, nice, and pretty girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:59.56,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.49,0:15:02.67,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,An earnest girl who's \Neasy to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:05.54,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they don't have a weird \Nchemical reaction and explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:06.71,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck to you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:08.85,Default,Takai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:12.16,Default,Taka,0000,0000,0000,,To the left, there's the \Ngeneral studies building,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.16,0:15:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and to the right is the music building.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:17.81,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,On the left is the general studies...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.37,0:15:19.95,Default,Taka,0000,0000,0000,,This is the inner courtyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.95,0:15:21.84,Default,Taka,0000,0000,0000,,If you're out here eating, \Nwatch out for black kites.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.84,0:15:22.58,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.58,0:15:23.81,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out for black kites.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:26.32,Default,Taka,0000,0000,0000,,And that's the gym over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:28.74,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,That is the gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:30.22,Default,Taka,0000,0000,0000,,Do you bike here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.22,0:15:31.49,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Do I what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:34.32,Default,Taka,0000,0000,0000,,Do you ride your \Nbike to come to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.32,0:15:36.37,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, I come by train.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:38.54,Default,Taka,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess I don't have \Nto show you the bike rack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.54,0:15:40.46,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,My club starts soon, so I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:41.34,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:44.03,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:49.51,Default,Taka,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should look into \Ngetting a different book.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.46,0:15:55.04,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Ki no Tsurayuki wrote about \Na ficticious woman who,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.04,0:15:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on her travels, met many...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:16:00.29,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then let's stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:03.52,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Starting next week, a new \Nstudent will be joining our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:04.36,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:06.42,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:10.58,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Sakai-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.58,0:16:12.15,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Let's walk home together part way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:18.79,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,The uniforms for the music \Nstudents are really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:19.75,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:24.31,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Do you ride your bike when it rains, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.31,0:16:25.89,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Usually.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.36,0:16:30.17,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:31.88,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.23,0:16:34.34,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,We've never walked home together before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:39.50,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well, I've been \Nwanting to get to know you better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:41.98,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,You quit the choir club, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:43.58,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:45.27,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:46.82,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:55.95,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,That's so embarassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:57.03,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.77,0:17:01.34,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,I overwrote the shame, \Nso none of it would be left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.34,0:17:02.91,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:04.25,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:08.94,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,I want to start a new choir club.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.94,0:17:10.61,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Our school is coordinating the joint
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,recital this year, so I think if \NI talk to the principal directly,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:15.71,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,I might have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.37,0:17:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering if you'd be interested in–
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:19.43,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:20.44,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:24.39,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not. I stopped singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:26.84,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is this because of your \Nsupplementary classes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.84,0:17:29.07,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have to have \Nrehearsals every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.07,0:17:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm sure you'd be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:33.58,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's a crazy challenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I think if we sing together,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it could lead to something incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:37.90,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:39.12,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,It would be so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:41.95,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Starting to sing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:45.36,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.36,0:17:46.64,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.64,0:17:47.98,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,If you pretend it's fun, it might
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,actually become fun after a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.86,0:17:51.33,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,If you just want to sing for fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why don't you go to \Nkaraoke or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:54.67,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Don't involve me in your games!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:00.51,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.79,0:18:01.93,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Then what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:02.97,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,What do you sing for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:05.82,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:08.16,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever! Just because you're having fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.16,0:18:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it doesn't mean you're not serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:11.55,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't answer my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:12.81,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dead serious about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.81,0:18:14.46,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe so, but don't get me involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:21.91,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to regret \Ngiving up before I even tried!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:31.22,Default,Voice1,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By the way, I heard that \Nyou're crazy about sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.22,0:18:34.92,Default,Voice2,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right! Especially homemade ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:50.65,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, Dora.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:11.96,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Makoto, you're not in any clubs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:14.25,Default,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just barge in here, you hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:17.42,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm making a choir club. \NYou'll join, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:18.72,Default,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:20.20,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,I left the application form on your desk,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so just fill it out and \Nbring it back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:24.56,Default,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of my room!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:26.69,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't bring me \Nback that application,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.69,0:19:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to tell mom about \Nyour secret porn stash.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:31.44,Default,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.83,0:19:35.43,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dear Yang:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.33,0:19:38.75,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've started at my new school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:42.70,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I tried to prepare as \Nmuch as possible, by reading books,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:44.75,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but Japanese customs \Nare quite complicated,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.75,0:19:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and it's not easy to avoid mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.02,0:19:49.87,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to try hard to make Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}feel like my home again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.22,0:19:55.03,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hope I can show you Japan, someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.14,0:19:58.97,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When that time comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.21,0:20:02.97,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Two more people, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:06.04,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Starting a club is fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.04,0:20:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but are you really sure you \Nwant to perform at the recital?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.79,0:20:09.73,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to be hard \Nto find members now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.13,0:20:11.23,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,You know that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:16.82,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Is this because you made Sakai-san mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.02,0:20:20.88,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Or is it what the vice \Nprincipal said to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.52,0:20:23.70,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, both.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.23,0:20:29.71,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you really did screw \Nup at last year's recital.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.07,0:20:33.81,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,It's not funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.81,0:20:36.40,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've been doing \Nall this different training.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.40,0:20:38.55,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not that person anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:39.48,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have some cream, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:40.63,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.04,0:20:43.93,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you, loud and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:46.10,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to go practice \Ntoday too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:47.62,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:49.34,Default,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,This one's on you.
