Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.73,0:23:29.82,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.86,0:23:33.22,Default,Taka,0000,0000,0000,,Were you just singing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.22,0:23:34.81,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,So this is sukiyaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.81,0:23:36.02,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Two cakes, please.
